A ranch style home surrounded by lush greenery.  

00:00:50:80 - 00:01:00:19 (00:00:09:38)
In the kitchen, wearing a long formal dress Dorothy slowly turns around in place as Sophia measures the hem. 

00:01:19:81 - 00:01:22:80 (00:00:02:98)
Blanch enters carrying a dress

00:02:17:61 - 00:02:20:00 (00:00:02:38)
Dorothy glares at Blanche.

Rose enters the kitchen.

00:03:42:52 - 00:03:55:66 (00:00:13:14
In the family room, Blanch, Dorothy and Rose sit on the couch wearing pajamas.  Blanche covers her eyes. Dorothy covers her ears. Rose covers her mouth. 

00:04:39:70 - 00:04:42:86 (00:00:03:15)
Blanche looks in a compact mirror.

00:05:18:84 - 00:05:21:32 (00:00:02:47)
Sophia opens the door. 

00:06:17:11 - 00:06:19:50 (00:00:02:38)
The dr. checks Blanches throat.

00:06:40:22 - 00:06:43:89 (00:00:03:66)
Blanche pushes the Dr.'s hand away and stares.

00:06:48:32 
The Dr. moves to Dorothy and checks her neck. 

00:09:13:12 - 00:09:19:01 (00:00:05:88)
Alone in the family room, Dorothy lays on the couch under a blanket. Blanche walks in. 

00:09:34:90 - 00:09:42:50 (00:00:07:59)
Blanche holds up an electrical cord extending from under the blanket. Blanche and Dorothy glare at each other.

00:11:24:21 - 00:11:27:71 (00:00:03:49)
Rose gives Dorothy a sip from her mug.

00:11:36:47 - 00:11:38:95 (00:00:02:47)
Rose sits down in the chair. 

00:11:50:55 - 00:11:53:19 (00:00:02:64)
Dorothy glares at Rose.

00:13:26:64 - 00:13:30:48 (00:00:03:83)
Rose, Blanche, and Dorothy march out. 

00:13:42:81 - 00:13:50:83 (00:00:08:02)
Dorothy sits in the kitchen drinking orange juice. Rose enters and opens the refrigerator. 

00:14:00:90 - 00:14:06:37 (00:00:05:46)
Dorothy pours the remaining orange juice from a pitcher into her glass. 

00:14:10:94 - 00:14:13:16 (00:00:02:21)
Blanche enters. 

00:15:00:84 - 00:15:03:32 (00:00:02:47)
Rose's face crumples. 

00:15:36:38 - 00:15:37:91 (00:00:01:53)
They hug.

00:15:46:56 - 00:15:49:47 (00:00:02:90)
They stop hugging and move apart.

00:18:15:62 - 00:18:17:42 (00:00:01:79)
Dorothy glares. 

00:18:24:88 - 00:18:27:61 (00:00:02:73)
Dorothy glares after Sophia.

00:18:28:07 - 00:18:34:47 (00:00:06:40)
At the banquet, Dorothy and Rose sit with their dates. Rose holds a tissue to her face. 

00:18:53:08 - 00:18:55:47 (00:00:02:38)
Dorothy’s date moves his salad. 

00:19:01:92 - 00:19:04:31 (00:00:02:38)
Blanche enters and sits down.

00:19:49:85 - 00:19:53:35 (00:00:03:49)
Sophia and Raul sit down at the table.

00:21:02:56 - 00:21:04:69 (00:00:02:13)
Dorothy stares at Blanche.

00:21:12:69 - 00:21:14:82 (00:00:02:13)
Blanch looks down.

00:21:23:67 - 00:21:28:11 (00:00:04:43)
Blanche holds out her hand. Tommy gives her money, then leaves. 

00:21:42:63 - 00:21:46:39 (00:00:03:75)
Blanche leans forward with wide eyes and a  tight mouth.

00:22:51:49 - 00:22:54:99 (00:00:03:49)
A woman walks out holding up a white suit.

00:23:20:90 - 00:23:24:40 (00:00:03:49)
The emcee opens an envelope and pulls out a card.

00:23:29:35 - 00:23:44:62 (00:00:15:27)
Sophia stands up, kisses always smiling Raul,  steps toward the podeum, turns around and kisses Raul again, then ascends the podeum and is handed a golden cup trophy.

Raul stands up and blows Sophia a kiss.
